ee15c3f-01:Deu:30:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"LXX reads If you obey the commands of the Lord your God that"},{"kind":"text","text":" I am commanding you today to love the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God, to walk in his ways, and to keep his commands, statutes, and ordinances, so that you may live "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"LXX reads ordinances, then you will live"},{"kind":"text","text":" and multiply, and the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God may bless you in the land you are entering to possess. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"LXX reads If you obey the commands of the Lord your God that"},{"marker":2,"text":"LXX reads ordinances, then you will live"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:30:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But if your heart turns away and you do not listen and you are led astray to bow in worship to other gods and serve them, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:30:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I tell you today that you will certainly perish and will not prolong your days in the land you are entering to possess across the Jordan. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:30:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I call heaven and earth as witnesses against you today that I have set before you life and death, blessing and curse. Choose life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 4:1","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:33","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 6:24","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 8:1","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 8:3","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 16:20","book":"Deu","chapter":16,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:46–47","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":46,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that you and your descendants may live, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 4:1","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"Dt 5:33","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":33},{"label":"Dt 6:24","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":24},{"label":"Dt 8:1","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Dt 8:3","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":3},{"label":"Dt 16:20","book":"Deu","chapter":16,"verse":20},{"label":"Dt 32:46–47","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":46}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:30:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"love the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God, obey him, and remain faithful "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit and hold on"},{"kind":"text","text":" to him. For he is your life, and he will prolong your days as you live in the land the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" swore to give to your ancestors "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 1:35","book":"Deu","chapter":1,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 1:35","book":"Deu","chapter":1,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit and hold on"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279365162}